"></span></p><p>據 Apple 發佈指，M2 MacBook Air 將會在 7 月 8 日晚上 8 點（香港時間）開始在 Apple 網上商店接受訂購，而正式的發售和出貨日期將會是 7 月 15 日。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Apple-MacBook-Air-M2-availability-July-2022-4up-colors_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg" alt="" width="1960" height="1306" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1108834" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Apple-MacBook-Air-M2-availability-July-2022-4up-colors_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1960w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Apple-MacBook-Air-M2-availability-July-2022-4up-colors_big.jpg.large_2x-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Apple-MacBook-Air-M2-availability-July-2022-4up-colors_big.jpg.large_2x-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Apple-MacBook-Air-M2-availability-July-2022-4up-colors_big.jpg.large_2x-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Apple-MacBook-Air-M2-availability-July-2022-4up-colors_big.jpg.large_2x-1536x1023.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>新款 M2 MacBook Air 除了採用最新的處理器之外，外形也是全新設計，類似 14 和 16 吋 MacBook Air 的方正風格，配有 4 個顏色可以選擇，包括午夜暗色、星光色、銀色和太空灰，售價由 HK$9,499 起。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2022/07/all-new-macbook-air-with-m2-available-to-order-starting-friday-july-8/">Apple</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-ove