</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>動漫電玩節 NFT 優先入場門票，發售詳情 + 五款設計</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/07/06/acghk-2022/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=acghk-2022</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[王希雯]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 06 Jul 2022 06:19:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[NFT]]></category><category><![CDATA[香港動漫電玩節]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1108356</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>第 23 屆香港動漫電玩節（ ACGHK 2022 ）即將開幕，由 7 月 29 日至 8 月 2 日一連五日 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>第 23 屆香港動漫電玩節（ ACGHK 2022 ）即將開幕，由 7 月 29 日至 8 月 2 日一連五日於灣仔會展舉行。作為一年一度的動漫電玩盛事當然要緊貼潮流，是次展覽展場內設立了全港首個大型元宇宙展覽項目，展覽多個創意商品，更推出可優先入場的 NFT 門票。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1108374 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.19.21-582x580.png" alt="" width="582" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.19.21-582x580.png 582w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.19.21-904x900.png 904w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.19.21-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.19.21-768x765.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.19.21.png 982w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 582px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1108375 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.20.23-579x580.png" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.20.23-579x580.png 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.20.23-898x900.png 898w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/螢幕截圖-2022-07-05-下午 1.20.23-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.h